Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.49,0:03:11.21,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Pulling, dragged me deep
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.71,0:03:14.63,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}All my body exposed
