Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.68,0:03:23.68,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Numb your senses
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.68,0:03:26.43,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}No fairness is needed for pigs
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.85,0:03:29.52,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Laughters above
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.56,0:03:32.14,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Playful smiles
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.19,0:03:34.73,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Die get rolled
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.81,0:03:37.11,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Bathe in sorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.15,0:03:41.03,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}My tomorrow is built upon your flesh
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.07,0:03:42.61,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Slay the last of your kind
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.70,0:03:50.62,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}To reclaim what's rightfully mine
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.45,0:03:46.66,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\fs-1\pos(640,673)}Each time we'll enter
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.78,0:03:48.08,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\fs-1\pos(640,673)}First time to make this
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.20,0:03:50.70,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\fs-1\pos(640,673)}Final dungeon 無念な未来の
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.79,0:03:52.04,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}I have a reason
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.12,0:03:53.33,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Don't part the rivers
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.46,0:03:56.04,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Surround them, off with their heads
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.13,0:03:57.34,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Christen my motive
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.38,0:03:58.63,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}First time to notice
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.67,0:04:01.30,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Final dungeon 群れて迷おう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.30,0:04:02.59,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}I hide among you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.59,0:04:03.59,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Facing my fire
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.63,0:04:07.97,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}At night I'm dreaming 永い夢の言葉
